      "desc": "When a birth parent contests an adoption, you need an experienced litigator in your corner. We're not afraid of courtrooms.",
      "full": "Contested adoptions arise when a birth parent disputes the termination of their parental rights. These cases require skilled legal strategy and courtroom advocacy. Attorney Harlow has extensive experience litigating contested adoptions in Tennessee courts."
